  "description": "Beautiful on the outside and powerful on the inside. You can trust this refrigerator to store your favorite products and gourmet dishes. The cooling system of the <b>MultiAirflow unit</b> uses <b>multi-flow distribution</b>. With this technology, the cold is directed to each shelf and each drawer individually. An interesting feature of the model is the use of <b>EasyAccess glass shelves</b>. Such shelves have a <b>retractable mechanism</b>, making it easy to get to those products that are in the back row. The Siemens KG39NXX316 refrigerator allows you to cool and freeze fresh food in <b>intensive mode</b>. The <b>fast freezing</b> and <b>fast cooling functions</b> can be activated by pressing the respective buttons. In this case, the performance of the refrigeration system will increase significantly, which will keep the old products cold. A high level of energy efficiency goes well with a good capacity. The share of the usable space of the refrigerator reaches <b>366 liters</b>, provided that the electricity consumption corresponds to class <b>A ++</b>. This model is characterized by consumption of <b>273 kWh annually</b>. This is an economical unit with high performance. The freezer compartment easily handles with the preparation of <b>14 kg of food per day</b>.",
